# RBAC × SpiceDB (server) — application-registry permissions (endpoints/pages/components)
# Requires: make up + make seed. Same dataset/IDs as cedar.rbac.http — decisions must match.

@host = http://localhost:8080
@spicedb = http://localhost:8443
@key = benchkey

### ALLOW — via facade (engine=spicedb → minimize_latency, SpiceDB's production default)
POST {{host}}/v1/authorize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "engine": "spicedb",
  "model": "rbac",
  "principal": "psn-000449",
  "action": "render",
  "resource_type": "Component",
  "resource": "cmp/hr/attendance-board/daily-grid"
}

### ALLOW — via facade, cache-bypassing consistency
POST {{host}}/v1/authorize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "engine": "spicedb-fully_consistent",
  "model": "rbac",
  "principal": "psn-000449",
  "action": "render",
  "resource_type": "Component",
  "resource": "cmp/hr/attendance-board/daily-grid"
}

### DENY — via facade
POST {{host}}/v1/authorize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "engine": "spicedb",
  "model": "rbac",
  "principal": "psn-000449",
  "action": "render",
  "resource_type": "Component",
  "resource": "cmp/hr/payroll-run/adjustment-editor"
}

### RAW — SpiceDB HTTP gateway, no code from this repo involved
POST {{spicedb}}/v1/permissions/check
Authorization: Bearer {{key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "consistency": { "fullyConsistent": true },
  "resource": { "objectType": "component", "objectId": "cmp/hr/attendance-board/daily-grid" },
  "permission": "render",
  "subject": { "object": { "objectType": "persona", "objectId": "psn-000449" } }
}
